description.narrative: UNICEF health staff efficiently contributed to health programming and monitored effectively to achieve planned results despite challenges posed by COVID-19. All planned activities were on track, with 100 per cent utilization of allocated funds and no over-six or over-nine-month DCT by end-2020. Hundred per cent HACT assurance and programme monitoring visits were ensured through online processes, and donor reports were submitted on time.
